Source.Name: python-pythran
Source.Summary: Ahead of Time compiler for numeric kernels
Source.Description: Pythran is an ahead of time compiler for a subset of the Python language, with a focus on scientific computing. It takes a Python module annotated with a few interface descriptions and turns it into a native Python module with the same interface, but (hopefully) faster.
